posts.post_content:
Posted By: Ray Piskadlo
I have a few CJs and other interesting cards/original photos available to trade for fair/poor T206 Commmons with backs other than Sweet Cap or Piedmont...

Here is what I have:

1914 CJ Alexander
1911 T205 Mathewson
1911 D304 Marquard
